Lornah Kiplagat held the third exhibition of her sportswear last Saturday at Galleria shopping mall, Langata. The 2017 Lornah Collection is a vivid mix of authentic African craft, earthly colours, natural patterns and refined high-tech elements. It comes with different categories: the Imani Jacket, Makena capri tight, Kibibi tank top, Afya shorts, Aziza sports shirts, Fahari sports bra and Zawadi long tights.The brand is supported by renowned Kenyan athletes Nixon Chepseba and Asbel Kiprop.